must make sure that we do not create incentives that contribute to 
unnecessary utilization and overspending she said 
the bush administration is conducting a review of the quality 
accessibility and cost of the nations health care system health 
and human services secretary louis sullivan who is leading the 
review has not said what changes he will recommend but he has 
rejected national health insurance as a solution 
