laboratories are foreigners who were let in only on condition they 
return home when their projects are done 
there is evidence that asian scientists who have become us 
citizens are going back to their native countries in growing 
numbers because of better opportunities said philip e schambra 
director of the fogarty international center at the national 
institutes of health 
