the 28gallon tank of his 1969 oldsmobile to avoid the tax hike he 
owns four cars but prefers the old 10mileagallon guzzler 
not everyone was so concerned 
customers arent too worried about it when youve got a bmw 
you dont worry if it costs 3 more to fill up the tank said 
jeffrey masko a service station cashier in the highrent pacific 
heights neighborhood of san francisco 
