with the tidal wave of insolvencies 
the bill would increase the maximum prison terms up to life in 
prison for the worst offenders and boost fines that could be 
levied against individuals and institutions convicted of savings 
and loan crimes 
it also would create new felony categories to close loopholes 
for those who conceal assets from the government or who try to 
