actually spiders cant be trained in the traditional sense like 
dogs cats bears or dolphins they dont sit up and beg or jump 
through hoops for food or rewards but there are tricks to control 
the eightlegged extras 
in arachnophobia invisible vibrating wires set up 
boundaries that the spiders wouldnt cross moviemakers also 
corralled spiders with the spray wax lemon pledge which the 
hairylegged spiders wouldnt walk in 
heat made the spiders active and blow dryers coaxed them to 
walk 
kutcher travels with a cache of six tarantulas that means he 
